NAME
    Template::Plugin::Calendar::Simple - TT plugin for Calendar::Simple

INSTALL
    Installation as usual:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

DESCRIPTION
    See perldoc Template::Plugin::Calendar::Simple

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Template-Toolkit
  Calendar::Simple;

